---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets'
import ContactSection from '../components/ContactSection.astro'
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout
  title="About Maggi Maid | Senior Home Help in Bradford"
  description="Discover Maggi Maid, a trusted one-to-one home help service for seniors in Bradford—focused on care, comfort, and independence."
>
  <div id="about" class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="topper">About Me</h1>

      <section>
        <h2 class="h2 heading has-underline">
          I've Been Where You Are - Let's Make It Easier
        </h2>

        <Image
          src={import('../assets/images/about-me-photo.jpg')}
          alt="Margaret, owner of Maggi Maid, with her mum and nephew."
          widths={[380 * 1.75, 1152, 1152 * 2]}
          sizes="min(calc(76rem - 4rem), calc(100vw - 2rem))"
          class="photo"
          loading="eager"
        />

        <div class="card">
          <p>Hi, I'm Margaret!</p>

          <p>
            For over 30 years, I've been the steady pair of hands families rely
            on. As a childminder raising my own three kids (and later, dozens of
            others), I learned that real care means showing up—not just
            physically, but emotionally. Now, I bring that same dedication to
            helping seniors stay independent at home.
          </p>

          <p>
            After walking alongside my mum through her later years. I understand
            how complicated it gets when someone needs help but doesn't want to
            admit it, or when everyday tasks start feeling overwhelming.
          </p>

          <p>
            That's why I offer straightforward home help here in Bradford. No
            big agency with rotating staff - just me showing up when I say I
            will, helping with shopping, meals around the house, getting to
            appointments, or simply being good company. I'm DBS-checked and
            properly trained, but more importantly, I approach this work like I
            did with my childminding - noticing what needs doing without being
            asked, respecting how people like things done, and showing up
            consistently.
          </p>

          <p>
            It's not about grand gestures. Just practical help from someone
            who's been there with her own family.
          </p>

          <p>
            (Please note: I don't provide personal care like bathing or
            medication.)
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="certificates">
          <div class="certificate-wrapper">
            <Image
              src={import('../assets/images/dbs-checked-certificate.png')}
              alt="DBS Checked certificate"
              class="certificate"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="certificate-wrapper">
            <Image
              src={import('../assets/images/food-safe-certificate.png')}
              alt="Food Safe certificate"
              class="certificate"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="certificate-wrapper">
            <Image
              src={import(
                '../assets/images/adult-safeguarding-certificate.png'
              )}
              alt="Adult Safeguarding certificate"
              class="certificate"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>

  <ContactSection />
</Layout>

<style lang="scss">
  #about {
    background-color: var(--colour-primary);
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .topper {
    font-style: italic;
    font-family: var(--font-family-base);
    font-size: var(--font-size-base);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-base);
    line-height: var(--line-height-base);
    color: rgba(var(--rgb-colour-text-base), 0.66);
  }

  .heading {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 30rem;
  }

  .photo {
    border-radius: 1.25rem;
    box-shadow: 0px 4px 11px 0px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
    margin-block: 2.5rem;
  }

  .card {
    max-width: 48rem;
    margin-inline: auto;
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 2rem 2rem 8rem;
    background-color: var(--colour-surface);
    box-shadow: 0px 8px 250px 0px rgba(27, 33, 62, 0.07);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .certificates {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: clamp(1rem, 3vw, 2rem);
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    padding-inline: 2rem;
  }

  .certificate-wrapper {
    border-radius: 9999px;
    background-color: var(--colour-surface);
    box-shadow: 0px 4px 31px 0px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
    max-width: 8rem;
    padding: clamp(1rem, 4vw, 2rem) clamp(0.5rem, 3vw, 1.5rem);
  }
</style>
